{"type":null,"faqId":22222,"title":"智联是什么？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<a name=\"interface_1_sec2_p1\"></a><span>智联是华为优化家庭组网和解决设备互联互通的专有解决方案，以支持智联特性的华为路由器为中心，构建家庭智联网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">便捷组网</span><span>：您可以通过“网线直连”、“Hi 按键一键配对”、“HiLink APP 智联”三种方式轻松将支持智联特性的华为路由器、华为Wi-Fi扩展器、华为Wi-Fi电力猫、华为OTT盒子和华为Wi-Fi音乐盒等设备加入已有的智联网络，组成覆盖更广的 Wi-Fi 网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">组网设备配置同步</span><span>：加入智联网络的所有设备，其组网配置可以通过华为主路由器的统一管理，包括Wi-Fi名称、密码、设备登录密码、Wi-Fi定时开关等。仅需修改华为主路由器的配置，就能达到修改所有组网设备配置的目的，便捷高效。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">Wi-Fi漫游</span><span>：智联网络内，所有设备的Wi-Fi名称、Wi-Fi密码自动与华为主路由器保持一致，用户在此Wi-Fi网络内移动时，智联网络能自动识别用户的位置变化，为用户选择最强最佳的Wi-Fi接入点，保证用户视频、语音、数据业务的流畅体验。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6083","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428566144000,"seriesProductName":"WS831-10","visitedTimes":99,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"WS831,荣耀路由","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}